<Author>josoMadrid
<Content>Fantastic rooms! I spent 3 days in the AC Victoria Suites on a business trip. The hotel is stunning! I was told that the hotel was fully refurbished last year 2007, and has now joined the hotel chain AC Hotels. It has 50 suites, with excellent design. The employees are very helpful. I had dinner at the hotels restaurant, which is called the Neichel, and has a 1-star michelin...what a fantastic surprise. The hotel is not in the centre, but it is absolutelly the ideal place to relax, lay at the swimming pool and get a good sleep after a day walking through the busy Ramblas. 
