<Author>ali34
<Content>Excellent Hotel! Myself and my husband stayed at the Victoria Suites for a child free weekend! I would easily say it was a good 4* hotel. I am the type of person who thinks the hotel makes the holiday as on many occasions I have been let down with the standard of hotels in the past...I was very impressed with the size of the suite, nice decor and it was very clean.The staff spoke very little english but we managed to make ourselves understood. They were very friendly and always willing to help. Ordering a taxi was never any problem, where ever you wanted to be it always worked out 5 euros per journey.The hotel is situated in the business district, very close to Barcelona Football Stadium which is well worth a visit whether you are into football or not. There are a few bars and a nice restarent over the road (about 200 yards away).Overall a really good hotel... highly recommended, cant wait to go back! 
